 -- Driver patches directory --

 * This directory gives the patches required to compile the driver codes such
   that they can be used with wrap-PI.

 * Files:
   - espresso-5.0_ipi.patch: A diff file that can be used to edit the Quantum-Espresso 
      code so that it can be used as a driver.
   - cp2k-2.4.0_ipi.patch: A diff file that can be used to edit the CP2K
      code so that it can be used as a driver.
